#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn46.4"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn46.4:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 46 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 46 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.4:0.2"
msgid "1. Pabbatavagga "
msgstr "1. Mountains "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn46.4:0.3"
msgid "4. Vatthasutta "
msgstr "4. Clothes "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.71, sc1
msgctxt "sn46.4:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā sāriputto sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. "
msgstr "At one time Venerable Sāriputta was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "

msgctxt "sn46.4:1.2"
msgid "Tatra kho āyasmā sāriputto bhikkhū āmantesi: "
msgstr "There Sāriputta addressed the mendicants: "

msgctxt "sn46.4:1.3"
msgid "“āvuso bhikkhavo”ti. "
msgstr "“Reverends, mendicants!” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.4:1.4"
msgid "“Āvuso”ti kho te bhikkhū āyasmato sāriputtassa paccassosuṃ. "
msgstr "“Reverend,” they replied. "

msgctxt "sn46.4:1.5"
msgid "Āyasmā sāriputto etadavoca: "
msgstr "Sāriputta said this: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn46.4:2.1"
msgid "“Sattime, āvuso, bojjhaṅgā. "
msgstr "“There are these seven awakening factors. "

msgctxt "sn46.4:2.2"
msgid "Katame satta? "
msgstr "What seven? "

msgctxt "sn46.4:2.3"
msgid "Satisambojjhaṅgo, dhammavicayasambojjhaṅgo, vīriyasambojjhaṅgo, pītisambojjhaṅgo, passaddhisambojjhaṅgo, samādhisambojjhaṅgo, upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo—"
msgstr "The awakening factors of mindfulness, investigation of principles, energy, rapture, tranquility, immersion, and equanimity. "

msgctxt "sn46.4:2.4"
msgid "ime kho, āvuso, satta bojjhaṅgā. "
msgstr "These are the seven awakening factors. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.4:2.5"
msgid "Imesaṃ khvāhaṃ, āvuso, sattannaṃ bojjhaṅgānaṃ yena yena bojjhaṅgena ākaṅkhāmi pubbaṇhasamayaṃ viharituṃ, tena tena bojjhaṅgena pubbaṇhasamayaṃ viharāmi; "
msgstr "In the morning, I meditate on whichever of these seven awakening factors I want. "

msgctxt "sn46.4:2.6"
msgid "yena yena bojjhaṅgena ākaṅkhāmi majjhanhikaṃ samayaṃ viharituṃ, tena tena bojjhaṅgena majjhanhikaṃ samayaṃ viharāmi; "
msgstr "At midday, "

msgctxt "sn46.4:2.7"
msgid "yena yena bojjhaṅgena ākaṅkhāmi sāyanhasamayaṃ viharituṃ, tena tena bojjhaṅgena sāyanhasamayaṃ viharāmi. "
msgstr "and in the evening, I meditate on whichever of these seven awakening factors I want. "

msgctxt "sn46.4:2.8"
msgid "Satisambojjhaṅgo iti ce me, āvuso, hoti, ‘appamāṇo’ti me hoti, ‘susamāraddho’ti me hoti, tiṭṭhantañca naṃ ‘tiṭṭhatī’ti pajānāmi. "
msgstr "If it’s the awakening factor of mindfulness, I know that it’s limitless and that it’s properly implemented. While it remains I understand that it remains. "

msgctxt "sn46.4:2.9"
msgid "Sacepi me cavati, ‘idappaccayā me cavatī’ti pajānāmi … pe … "
msgstr "And if it subsides I understand that it subsides. … "

msgctxt "sn46.4:2.10"
msgid "upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo iti ce me, āvuso, hoti, ‘appamāṇo’ti me hoti, ‘susamāraddho’ti me hoti, tiṭṭhantañca naṃ ‘tiṭṭhatī’ti pajānāmi. "
msgstr "If it’s the awakening factor of equanimity, I know that it’s limitless and that it’s properly implemented. While it remains I understand that it remains. "

msgctxt "sn46.4:2.11"
msgid "Sacepi me cavati, ‘idappaccayā me cavatī’ti pajānāmi. "
msgstr "And if it subsides I understand that it subsides. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.72, sc3
msgctxt "sn46.4:3.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, āvuso, rañño vā rājamahāmattassa vā nānārattānaṃ dussānaṃ dussakaraṇḍako pūro assa. "
msgstr "Suppose that a ruler or their minister had a chest full of garments of different colors. "

msgctxt "sn46.4:3.2"
msgid "So yaññadeva dussayugaṃ ākaṅkheyya pubbaṇhasamayaṃ pārupituṃ, taṃ tadeva dussayugaṃ pubbaṇhasamayaṃ pārupeyya; "
msgstr "In the morning, they’d don whatever pair of garments they wanted. "

msgctxt "sn46.4:3.3"
msgid "yaññadeva dussayugaṃ ākaṅkheyya majjhanhikaṃ samayaṃ pārupituṃ, taṃ tadeva dussayugaṃ majjhanhikaṃ samayaṃ pārupeyya; "
msgstr "At midday, "

msgctxt "sn46.4:3.4"
msgid "yaññadeva dussayugaṃ ākaṅkheyya sāyanhasamayaṃ pārupituṃ, taṃ tadeva dussayugaṃ sāyanhasamayaṃ pārupeyya. "
msgstr "and in the evening, they’d don whatever pair of garments they wanted. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.4:3.5"
msgid "Evameva khvāhaṃ, āvuso, imesaṃ sattannaṃ bojjhaṅgānaṃ yena yena bojjhaṅgena ākaṅkhāmi pubbaṇhasamayaṃ viharituṃ, tena tena bojjhaṅgena pubbaṇhasamayaṃ viharāmi; "
msgstr "In the same way, in the morning, "

msgctxt "sn46.4:3.6"
msgid "yena yena bojjhaṅgena ākaṅkhāmi majjhanhikaṃ samayaṃ viharituṃ, tena tena bojjhaṅgena majjhanhikaṃ samayaṃ viharāmi; "
msgstr "at midday, "

msgctxt "sn46.4:3.7"
msgid "yena yena bojjhaṅgena ākaṅkhāmi sāyanhasamayaṃ viharituṃ, tena tena bojjhaṅgena sāyanhasamayaṃ viharāmi. "
msgstr "and in the evening, I meditate on whichever of these seven awakening factors I want. "

msgctxt "sn46.4:3.8"
msgid "Satisambojjhaṅgo iti ce me, āvuso, hoti, ‘appamāṇo’ti me hoti, ‘susamāraddho’ti me hoti, tiṭṭhantañca naṃ ‘tiṭṭhatī’ti pajānāmi. "
msgstr "If it’s the awakening factor of mindfulness, I know that it’s limitless and that it’s properly implemented. While it remains I understand that it remains. "

msgctxt "sn46.4:3.9"
msgid "Sacepi me cavati, ‘idappaccayā me cavatī’ti pajānāmi … pe … "
msgstr "And if it subsides I understand that it subsides. … "

msgctxt "sn46.4:3.10"
msgid "upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo iti ce me, āvuso, hoti, ‘appamāṇo’ti me hoti, ‘susamāraddho’ti me hoti, tiṭṭhantañca naṃ ‘tiṭṭhatī’ti pajānāmi. "
msgstr "If it’s the awakening factor of equanimity, I know that it’s limitless and that it’s properly implemented. While it remains I understand that it remains. "

msgctxt "sn46.4:3.11"
msgid "Sacepi me cavati, ‘idappaccayā me cavatī’ti pajānāmī”ti. "
msgstr "And if it subsides I understand that it subsides.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.4:3.12"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr ""

